outputs.output_descr:
Support the Inter-Ministerial Working Group (IMWG) on Decentralisation, in establishing a clearer and functional role, responsibilities and accompanying procedures;
•	Provision of on the job technical and advisory assistance to MLGA/IMWG;
•	Draft reports on necessary proceedings of IMWG;
•	Coordinate the follow-up activities of IMWG; 
 
Put in place a more effective central support system for inter-municipal cooperation and develop set of regulations on different cooperation modalities;
•	Conduct municipal consultations, and discuss findings with a wide range of stakeholders, including civil society, around modalities and scope for inter-municipal cooperation projects;
•	Assist the MLGA in establishing the framework for inter-municipal cooperation projects, and initiate the initial 1 or 2 pilot projects and codify lessons learned;
•	Undertake two study visits in neighbouring countries to review inter-municipal cooperation models

Support the newly created municipalities in establishing their development plans;
•	Organise expert mission(s) jointly with Bratislava Regional Centre and a local research institute in establishing the development plans and necessary development framework for implementation and sustainability;

 Support the municipalities in tracking public satisfaction with service delivery in each municipality (follow-up of Kosovo Mosaic 2004 and 2006 reports);

•	Conduct, jointly with MLGA, AKM and other stakeholders, the 3rd Kosovo Mosaic report on public satisfaction with public service delivery;
•	Organise follow-up discussion activities with municipal leader, citizens and other stakeholders. 
Strengthen coordination mechanisms for international assistance of municipal development, through establishment of aid coordination system in the MLGA.

•	Organise technical expert mission in identifying the most appropriate software solution for tracking the international assistance offered to MLGA and municipalities.
•	Organise training for MLGA and municipal users
•	Organise a comprehensive presentation for the donors and the government
